<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA514_05_IH_0001_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema514_05.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema514_05_ih_0001">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1" lang="y" class="fraction_box_title">
          <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">              
              <div class="fraction_box ml_0">
                <span>1</span>
                <span>2</span>
              </div>
              과
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>3</span>
                <span>4</span>
              </div>
              을 통분하려고 합니다. <span class="empty_box nemo"></span>안에 알맞은 수를 써넣으세요.
            </div>
          </div>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="flex justify_center">
          <div class="question_box">
            <div class="flex dir_col align_center gap_60">
              <div class="flex align_end gap_12">
                <div class="flex align_center gap_4">
                  <div class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>2</span></div>
                  =
                  <div class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>4</span></div>
                  =
                  <div class="fraction_box"><span>3</span><span>6</span></div>
                  =
                  <div class="fraction_box"><span>4</span><span>8</span></div>
                  =
                  <div class="fraction_box"><span>5</span><span>10</span></div>
                  = ...
                </div>
                ,
                <div class="flex align_center gap_4">
                  <div class="fraction_box"><span>3</span><span>4</span></div>
                  =
                  <div class="fraction_box"><span>6</span><span>8</span></div>
                  =
                  <div class="fraction_box"><span>9</span><span>12</span></div>
                  =
                  <div class="fraction_box"><span>12</span><span>16</span></div>
                  =
                  <div class="fraction_box"><span>15</span><span>20</span></div>
                  = ...
                </div>
              </div>
              <div lang="y" class="flex align_center gap_12">
                분모가 같은 분수끼리 짝 지으면
                <div class="bracket">
                  <span class="bracket-l"></span>
                  <div class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>4</span></div>
                  <span class="comma">,</span>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field></div>
                    <span>4</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="bracket-r"></span>
                  <span class="comma">,</span>
                </div>

                <div class="bracket">
                  <span class="bracket-l"></span>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field></div>
                    <span>8</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="comma">,</span>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="6"></math-field></div>
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="8"></math-field></div>
                  </div>
                  <span class="bracket-r"></span>
                </div>
                <span class="comma">,</span> ...입니다.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <div lang="y">
                  <div class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>2</span></div>
                  ,
                  <div class="fraction_box"><span>3</span><span>4</span></div>
                  과 크기가 같은 분수 중에서 분모가 같은 분수는
                  <div class="bracket">
                    <span class="bracket-l"></span>
                    <div class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>4</span></div>
                    <span class="comma">,</span>
                    <div class="fraction_box"><span>3</span><span>4</span></div>
                    <span class="bracket-r"></span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="ml-8">,</span>
                  <div class="bracket">
                    <span class="bracket-l"></span>
                    <div class="fraction_box"><span>4</span><span>8</span></div>
                    <span class="comma">,</span>
                    <div class="fraction_box"><span>6</span><span>8</span></div>
                    <span class="bracket-r"></span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="ml-8">,</span> ...입니다.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key" lang="y">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
